    "body": "## Summary\n\n- Prevent `CleanIndices` from deleting old backing indices while incremental reindex catch-up is still in progress by loading protected physical indices from Phase 1 and catch-up upgrade state\n- Add per-index `CatchUpStatus` tracking to `IncrementalReindexCatchUpStep` with checkpoint persistence, early exit when catch-up is complete, and improved error handling for timeseries gap reindex (including skipping missing indices)\n- Order non-blocking upgrades so incremental reindex runs before orphan cleanup (`@Order(4)` vs `@Order(100)`)\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] `./gradlew spotlessApply`\n- [x] `./gradlew :datahub-upgrade:test --tests \"com.linkedin.datahub.upgrade.system.elasticsearch.steps.*\"`\n- [x] `./gradlew :metadata-io:test --tests \"com.linkedin.metadata.search.elasticsearch.indexbuilder.IncrementalReindexStateTest\" --tests \"com.linkedin.metadata.search.indexbuilder.ESIndexBuilderTest.testCleanIndex*\"`\n\n\nMade with [Cursor](https://cursor.com)",
